Ing '''Sanya''' ({{zh|s=三亚 |t=三亞 |p=Sānyà}}) metung ya kareng atlung [[lakanbalen a kadaneng prefecture]] (''prefecture-level city'') king lalawigan ning  [[Hainan]] ampo ing pekamarayu king [[mauli]]ng lakanbalen king islang lalawigan. Agpang king 2010 Census, ing populasyun ning Sanya 685,408 ya katau,<ref>{{zh icon}} Compilation by LianXin website. [http://www.luqyu.cn/tongjishow.asp?tid=949 Data from the Sixth National Population Census of the People's Republic of China]</ref> a manuknangan king lapad a {{convert|1919.58|km²|sp=uk}}. Pikabalwan ya ing lakabalen king kayang klimang tropical at megi yang sikat a pupuntalan da reng turista, ampong sanayan ning koponan nang pambangsa ning Tsina king [[beach volleyball]]. Ing Sanya ing lugal nung nu la manuknangan da reng mangalating grupu da reng taung lahing [[Utsul]].

